# Orion Insta — Advanced GPT with RAG, Image & Voice AI Assistant

Orion Insta is an advanced multimodal AI assistant built with:
- Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
- Image understanding & generation
- Voice input + AI speech output
- Intelligent chat with memory
- Fast, modern UI

It acts as a personal AI assistant capable of analyzing images, responding through voice, using custom knowledge sources, and generating high-quality answers.

---

## Features

### 1. Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
- Upload documents (PDF, text, etc.)
- AI answers using your data
- Automatic text chunking + embeddings
- Vector search for accurate context
- Multi-document support

### 2. Voice Input & Voice Output
- Speak into the mic → converts your speech to text
- AI replies using realistic speech
- Uses Whisper / STT + natural TTS

### 3. Image Understanding + Image Generation
- Upload images → AI explains & analyzes them
- Extracts text, objects, and context
- Generate new AI images from prompts
- Multimodal GPT reasoning

### 4. Smart AI Chat with Memory
- Saves context over long conversations
- Learns from previous interactions
- Clean and fast real-time UI
- Streaming responses

### 5. Advanced GPT Integration
- GPT-4 / GPT-4o / GPT-5 style reasoning
- Function calling support
- Structured outputs
- Multi-modal support

---

## Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React / Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Zustand
- Axios
- Web Speech API

### Backend
- Node.js / Express
- LangChain / Custom RAG pipeline
- Vector DB (FAISS / Pinecone / Chroma)
- OpenAI API (GPT, Images, Audio)
- Whisper / TTS
- JWT Auth

---

