---

## Setup Instructions

### Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/me_priyansshh/orion
cd orion-insta
```

### Start Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Start Backend
```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm start
```

---

## Environment Variables (.env.example)

```
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key_here
VECTOR_DB_URL=
JWT_SECRET=
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173
```

